 Encke central ringlet, the observed\nasymmetry is mainly due to the combined action of plasma drag and Pan's gravity\ncausing a focusing of dust in the region leading Pan's orbit (Hedman et al.\n2013).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2015 00:22:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
