en they have\npoor quality, although the behaviour of these methods when confronted with\nregions that have different properties and different values of N/O should be\nexplored.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2015 02:54:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2015 22:44:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-02"}
